'''塞梅魯火山'''（{{lang-id|Gunung Semeru}}）是[[印度尼西亞|印度尼西亞]]的[[火山|火山]]，位於[[爪哇島|爪哇島]]東南部，行政方面由[[東爪哇省|東爪哇省]]負責管轄，海拔高度3,676米，是爪哇島最高的山峰，自1818年有55次[[火山爆發|火山爆發]]的記綠，造成[[熔岩|熔岩流]]和[[火山碎屑流|火山碎屑流]]，所有爆發的強度為[[火山爆發指數|火山爆發指數]]2至3級。

== 2021年噴發 ==
2021年12月4日，塞梅鲁火山於該年第二次喷发（首次於2021年1月）<ref name=sfchron20211204>{{cite news |date=2021-12-04 |title=Indonesia's Semeru volcano erupts, spews huge ash cloud |url=https://www.sfchronicle.com/news/article/Indonesia-s-Semeru-volcano-erupts-spews-huge-ash-16674216.php |access-date=2021-12-04 |work=[[San_Francisco_Chronicle|San Francisco Chronicle]] |archive-date=2021-12-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211204134421/https://www.sfchronicle.com/news/article/Indonesia-s-Semeru-volcano-erupts-spews-huge-ash-16674216.php }}</ref>，並於同月6日發生第三次噴發。<ref>{{Cite web|last=Kurniawan|first=Willy|last2=Adriansyah|first2=Tommy|last3=Dec. 6|first3=Reuters {{!}} Posted-|last4=A.m|first4=2021 at 7:17|title=Indonesia volcano erupts again as death toll rises to 22|url=https://www.ksl.com/article/50301895/indonesia-volcano-erupts-again-as-death-toll-rises-to-22|access-date=2021-12-06|website=www.ksl.com|language=en|archive-date=2021-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211206185808/https://www.ksl.com/article/50301895/indonesia-volcano-erupts-again-as-death-toll-rises-to-22}}</ref>

